ol, England":"бристол, Англия","lifeSummary":"Когда Elizabeth Young родилась в 1441 г. в местности бристол, Англия, её отцу по имени Thomas Young было 30 лет, а матери, которую звали Isabell Young, 29. Она вышла замуж за человека по имени John Newdegate. У них был по крайней мере 1 сын. Она умерла в 1488 г. в местности Англия, Великобритания в возрасте 47 лет и была похоронена в местности астли, варвиккшир, Англия."},"sm":{"1441–1488":"1441–1488","1435–1499":"1435–1499","1461–1528":"1461–1528","1411–Male":"1411–Ua Maliu","1412–Female":"1412–Ua Maliu","1435":"1435","1412":"1412","1488":"1488","1455":"1455","1411":"1411","1499":"1499","1441":"1441","1461":"1461","19 September 1488":"19 Setema 1488","1528":"1528","Astley, Warwickshire, England":"Astley, Warwickshire, Egelani","England":"Egelani, United Kingdom","Bristol, England":"Bristol, Egelani"},"sk":{"1441–1488":"1441–1488","1435–1499":"1435–1499","1461–1528":"1461–1528","1411–Male":"1411–Zosnulý","1412–Female":"1412–Zosnulá","1435":"1435","1412":"1412","1488":"1488","1455":"1455","1411":"1411","1499":"1499","1441":"1441","1461":"1461","19 September 1488":"19. september 1488","1528":"1528","Astley, Warwickshire, England":"Astley, Warwickshire, England","England":"Anglicko, Spojené kráľovstvo","Bristol, England":"Bristol, England"},"es":{"1441–1488":"1441–1488","1435–1499":"1435–1499","1461–1528":"1461–1528","1411–Male":"1411–Fallecido","1412–Female":"1412–Fallecida","1435":"1435","1412":"1412","1488":"1488","1455":"1455","1411":"1411","1499":"1499","1441":"1441","1461":"1461","19 September 1488":"19 de septiembre de 1488","1528":"1528","Astley, Warwickshire, England":"Astley, Warwickshire, Inglaterra","England":"Inglaterra, Reino Unido","Bristol, England":"Bristol, Inglaterra","lifeSummary":"Cuando Elizabeth Young nació en 1441, en Bristol, Inglaterra, su papá, Thomas Young, tenía 30 años y su mamá, Isabell Young, tenía 29 años. Se casó con John Newdegate. Fueron padres de por lo menos 1 hijo. Murió en 1488, en In